F = (v,p,t) -> A*v + [ϕ0(t);zeros(nx-2);ϕ1(t)]/h^2
x = range(0,1,nx + 2)
prob = ODEProblem(F, f.(x[2:end-1]), (0.0, T));
soln =  solve(prob, RK4(),abstol=1e-4);
tv = soln.t
nt = length(tv)
```

